channel.title: TryScape (NEW PROJECT!)
channel.description:
Hi, The Real Java here, i was thinking of making a new project called TryScape using a TestScape source. We will need about 2 more coders. If you know Java and would like to help post, but remember...No newbie's who don't know java... If you would like to help it would be a great example to post a tut that you have done..This will be a source not a server unless once it has been done people can make there own server using this source...And everyone who takes part in this will be given credit.
[s]We need 2 more coders... If i have accepted you as a good coder add ~ Skater_Ry@hotmail.co.uk ~ to msn. Look forward to working with you.[/s]
Thanks

~The Real Java~
